# Lottie animations directory (CHG-20260428-09)
#
# Reserved for AE → Bodymovin exports.
# Expected files (delivered by QY):
#   - about-story.json     (6-scene about page animation)
#
# Once a .json is dropped here, lottie-miniprogram in `usingComponents`
# of pages/about/about.json can be enabled, and about.wxml's existing
# .about-scene keyframes block (about.wxml:5-48) becomes the fallback.
#
# Prerequisite: run "工具 → 构建 npm" in WeChat DevTools to generate
# miniprogram_npm/lottie-miniprogram/ (cannot be done by Claude Code).
